---
---

<section id="about" class="section-wrap">

  <div class="reveal">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">
      <span class="section-num">01 / About</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="section-title">The operator<br/>behind the infra.</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="about-grid">

    <!-- Bio -->
    <div>
      <div class="reveal" data-delay="0.1s">
        <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--fg); line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 24px;">
          I'm a DevOps engineer designing and operating the cloud infrastructure
          that lets engineering teams ship faster and sleep better.
          <span style="color: var(--amber);">AWS Certified Solutions Architect</span>, day job at
          <a href="https://www.fundcraft.lu/" target="_blank" style="color: var(--fg); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-2); transition: border-color 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='var(--amber)'" onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='var(--border-2)'">Fundcraft</a>
          running a regulated fintech platform.
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--fg-2); line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 24px;">
          Right alongside the infra work, I'm deep in the AI side of engineering —
          running models locally, building agents, and rolling out coding assistants in production.
          I think the highest-leverage shift in our industry right now is thoughtful AI integration,
          and I want to be inside that loop, not watching it from the outside.
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--fg-2); line-height: 1.85;">
          Outside of work I run a full Kubernetes homelab on bare metal — Proxmox, K3s, TrueNAS —
          with a complete observability stack, self-hosted CI/CD, and a growing catalogue of
          personal projects (including <strong style="color: var(--fg); font-weight: 600;">Jarvis</strong>, my self-hosted assistant).
          I believe the best way to understand a technology is to operate it in production,
          even if that production is your basement.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Stats -->
      <div class="reveal" data-delay="0.2s" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1px; border: 1px solid var(--border); margin-top: 40px;">
        <div style="padding: 24px; border-right: 1px solid var(--border);">
          <div class="font-mono" style="font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--fg-2); margin-bottom: 8px;">Self-hosted services</div>
          <div style="font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 2.2rem; letter-spacing: -0.03em; color: var(--fg);">
            <span data-count="30" data-suffix="+">30+</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 24px;">
          <div class="font-mono" style="font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--fg-2); margin-bottom: 8px;">AWS Certification</div>
          <div style="font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 2.2rem; letter-spacing: -0.03em; color: var(--amber);">SAA</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Photo + card -->
    <div class="reveal" data-delay="0.15s" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px;">
      <!-- Profile photo -->
      <div style="position: relative;">
        <img
          src="/profile-long-shirt.png"
          alt="Francesc Barnola"
          class="profile-img"
        />
        <!-- Amber tint overlay on hover -->
        <div class="photo-overlay" style="position: absolute; inset: 0; background: var(--amber); opacity: 0; mix-blend-mode: multiply; transition: opacity 0.4s;"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Current role card -->
      <div style="border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 16px 20px; background: var(--bg-2);">
        <div class="font-mono" style="font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--fg-2); margin-bottom: 10px;">Currently at</div>
        <div style="font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--fg); margin-bottom: 2px;">Fundcraft</div>
        <div class="font-mono" style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--fg-2);">DevOps Engineer · Fintech</div>
        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; margin-top: 12px;">
          <span style="width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: #4ade80; display: inline-block;"></span>
          <span class="font-mono" style="font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--fg-2);">Active</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Location card -->
      <div style="border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 16px 20px; background: var(--bg-2);">
        <div class="font-mono" style="font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--fg-2); margin-bottom: 6px;">Location</div>
        <div style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--fg);">Girona / Barcelona</div>
        <div class="font-mono" style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--fg-2); margin-top: 2px;">Remote · On-site</div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 260px;
    gap: 56px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .profile-img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 60%;
    display: block;
    filter: grayscale(20%);
  }

  .photo-overlay { transition: opacity 0.4s ease; }
  div:has(> .photo-overlay):hover .photo-overlay { opacity: 0.12 !important; }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
    }
    /* Hide the photo column entirely on mobile — content first */
    .about-grid > div:last-child {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
